text: Nathan Donald Diaz (born April 16, 1985) in Stockton, California is an American mixed martial artist, He competes at the Lightweight and Welterweight division of the UFC. Before signing with the UFC, Diaz competed in World Extreme Cagefighting, Strikeforce, and Pancrase. He has been in the UFC since winning The Ultimate Fighter 5. == References == == Other websites == * Nate Diaz Profile at UFC.com * * * Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:american mixed martial artists
